-- Siemens, Shanghai Electric Sign $3.5 Billion Deal on Turbines, Xinhua Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-16T05:31:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/siemens-shanghai-electric-sign-3-5-billion-deal-on-turbines-xinhua-says.html

          
          
             Siemens AG and Shanghai Electric
Group Company Ltd. signed a $3.5 billion agreement for research
and development of steam and gas turbines, Xinhua News Agency
reported today, without saying where it obtained the
information.  
